  "page": "Trader Town",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:WorldofIceandFire.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Trader Town is located in The Known World\"><img alt=\"Trader Town is located in The Known World\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/10/WorldofIceandFire.png/400px-WorldofIceandFire.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"266\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/10/WorldofIceandFire.png/600px-WorldofIceandFire.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/10/WorldofIceandFire.png/800px-WorldofIceandFire.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 57.8%; left: 80%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Trader Town\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Trader Town</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a> and the location of Trader Town\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Trader Town</b> is a rude, sprawling garrison city of northern <a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a> in eastern <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The city lies east of the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Sand_Sea\" title=\"Great Sand Sea\">Great Sand Sea</a>, and west of the <a href=\"/index.php/Shrinking_Sea\" title=\"Shrinking Sea\">Shrinking Sea</a>. The vast <a href=\"/index.php/Plains_of_the_Jogos_Nhai\" title=\"Plains of the Jogos Nhai\">plains of the Jogos Nhai</a> are north of Trader Town. From <a href=\"/index.php/Kayakayanaya\" title=\"Kayakayanaya\">Kayakayanaya</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Steel_Road\" title=\"Steel Road\">Steel Road</a> skirts the topmost northern edge of the Great Sand Sea, and turns south to Trader Town. The city is connected to <a href=\"/index.php/Tiqui\" title=\"Tiqui\">Tiqui</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Bayasabhad\" title=\"Bayasabhad\">Bayasabhad</a> by the <a href=\"/index.php/Sand_Road\" title=\"Sand Road\">Sand Road</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Trader Town is the seat of General <a href=\"/index.php/Pol_Qo\" title=\"Pol Qo\">Pol Qo</a>, Hammer of the <a href=\"/index.php/Jogos_Nhai\" title=\"Jogos Nhai\">Jogos Nhai</a>, the self-proclaimed first <a href=\"/index.php/Orange_emperors\" title=\"Orange emperors\">orange emperor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Trader_Town&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"refere